page.title: 19RESIDENTIAL,HIGH WYCOMBE
page.content: Daws Hill Lane is residential.There are 51 detached houses in the lane all built on one side of the road.In one of these houses we talked to the owner who had lived there only six months.He lives there because it is handy for his printing business in High Wycombe.She is a beautician.They have about an acre of garden and two cars.Some of the people living in Daws Hill lane work in London.The houses are pleasant with large rooms and 4 or five bedrooms.The houses are opposite the American Air Base.
